item.title: Fake richness
item.dc:creator: @unlimitedorb unlimitedorb
item.description:
@unlimitedorb wrote:

Below is a Javascript URL to change the amount of neopoints you have (client side).
Have I made things better in this world? Probably not…but at least I wasn’t bored while doing it.

Step 1.) Copy and paste the code below into the address bar of any Neopets page.
(Must be logged in.)
Step 2.) Press Enter.

[code]javascript:
/**

  • Javascript url to change the number of neopoints.
  • (client side only!)
  • Author: unlimitedorb
    */
    var amount = “1,000,000,000”;
    var landmark = “http://neopets.com/objects.phtml?type=inventory”;
    var anchors = window.document.getElementsByTagName(“a”);
    var neopoints;
    for(var i = 0; i < anchors.length; i++) {
    if(anchors[i].href == landmark) {
    neopoints = anchors[i];
    break;
    }
    }
    void(neopoints.innerHTML = amount);[/code]

Default amount this will change your neopoints to is 1 trillion.
